{"word":"G1507 - εἱλίσσω - heilíssō - hi-lis'-so - Roll together","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">εἱλίσσω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">heilíssō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hi-lis'-so</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Roll together</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சுருட்டு"},{"paragraph":"to roll up or together"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>A prolonged form of a primary but defective verb <b>&#x03B5;&#x03B9;&#x0314;&#x0301;&#x03BB;&#x03C9;</b> <b>heilo&#x0304;</b> (of the same meaning); to <i>coil</i> or <i>wrap</i>: - roll together. See also <a href=\"#/G1667 - ἑλίσσω - helíssō - hel-is'-so/1667\">G1667</a>.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}